A group known as Patriots For the Reelection of Tambuwal, yesterday, said that Sokoto State stands a better chance of benefit more, if governor Aminu Waziri Tambuwal is return in 2019. The group in a statement signed by its chairman, Alhaji Umar Galadima, said the achievement of Tambuwal in Sokoto State is something they are proud. He added that, as Speaker of the House of Representatives, Tambuwal made the state proud. According to the group, it has become expedient on the electorates of Sokoto to give another chance to Governor Tambuwal, whose first term as governor brought peace and development. “We should not also forget so soon the governor’s commitment to the sustenance of democracy while he was the speaker of the House of Representatives where he made his make and made the people of Sokoto proud.”